    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="structhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1spawn_1_1SpawnContext" kindref="compound">SpawnContext</ref> aggregates all contextual information needed by SpawnPlacer and SpawnInitializer to configure a spawned entity. It may contain an <ref refid="structhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1spawn_1_1EmitterContext" kindref="compound">EmitterContext</ref> if the spawn was triggered by another entity.</para>
<para>Example usage: ```cpp <ref refid="structhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1spawn_1_1SpawnContext" kindref="compound">SpawnContext</ref> ctx; ctx.emitterContext = <ref refid="structhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1spawn_1_1EmitterContext" kindref="compound">EmitterContext</ref>{shipPos, shipVelocity};</para>
<para>placer-&gt;getPosition(guid, bounds, cursor, ctx); initializer-&gt;initialize(entity, cursor, ctx); ```</para>
